{{version030}}
{{flavour|Breathes a bolt of dispelling energy at a targeted creature, possibly removing some of its enchantments.}}

'''Quicksilver Bolt''' is a monster-only spell which fires a blast of irresistible, piercing, magic-dispelling energy. Any target struck by it will take significant damage and have the duration of their magical enhancements drastically reduced. See [[list of dispellable effects]] for the full list.

{{monsters with spell}}

Players can duplicate the effect with a [[wand of quicksilver]].

==History==
*In [[0.29]], the [[wand of quicksilver]] was introduced, allowing players (and more monsters) access to this spell.
*Prior to [[0.19]], quicksilver bolts did not pierce through enemies.
*Prior to [[0.18]], the spell could occasionally be cast by the player through the use of a [[Random Bolt]] spell, as evoked through a [[rod of destruction]].

[[Category:Monster spells]]
